\u2019ut Imam Ahmad commented, \u201cThe best of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6713,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/20\/khulafa-rashidun-khilafah-abu-bakr-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":43679,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: The Prophet\u2019s vision of Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhile I was sleeping, I saw myself standing at a well and upon it was a bucket. I drew water from the well as much as Allah willed. Then, Ibn Abi Quhafah, Abu Bakr, took the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43468,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/04\/04\/four-khulafa-rashidun\/","url_meta":{"origin":43679,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Khilafah: The Prophet foretells Four Righteous Caliphs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 4, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Safinah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Caliphate after me will last for thirty years, then there will be kingship.\u201d Sa\u2019id said to Safinah, \u201cCount the Caliphates of Abu Bakr, Umar, and Uthman?\u201d Then, Safinah said, \u201cYou must count the Caliphate of Ali.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context"